Bigman's helmet suddenly rang with sound as the call flooded his left-open radio receiver.\par
"Hey, Shortie, get moving. There's a ship coming in."\par
Bigman jumped at the noise and moved straight upward, limbs flailing. He yelled, "Who're you calling Shortie?"\par
