118 LUCKY STARR\par
Bigman said, "Well, what do we do?"\par
"Look around the neighborhood. It may take us a few days."\par
The path of the \i Shooting Starr \i0 grew erratic. It headed outward from the Sun, away from the forbidden zone and into the nearest constellation of asteroids. The gravities jumped their needles at the pull of distant mass.\par
