136 LUCKY STARR\par
However, this left room for higher concentrations, up to somewhat more than normal atmospheric pressure, before there was danger of toxic effects. Lucky let the oxygen pour into his suit.\par
Then, having done so, he closed the valve under his face-plate entirely and removed the cylinder.\par
